 style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0.3em 0.1em;line-height:14px;text-align:center;width:46.9792px\">18th</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0.3em 0.1em;line-height:14px;text-align:center;width:43.2917px\">+6</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0.3em 0.1em;line-height:14px;text-align:center;width:241.729px\">@Item[ssH2dak4NcVUCJDi]{Profound Insight}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;background-color:#e0e5c1\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0.3em 0.1em;line-height:14px;background-color:#e8e0ca;text-align:center;width:46.9792px\">19th</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0.3em 0.1em;line-height:14px;background-color:#e8e0ca;text-align:center;width:43.2917px\">+6</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0.3em 0.1em;line-height:14px;background-color:#e8e0ca;text-align:center;width:241.729px\">Ability Score Improvement</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact\">\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0.3em 0.1em;line-height:14px;text-align:center;width:46.9792px\">20th</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0.3em 0.1em;line-height:14px;text-align:center;width:43.2917px\">+6</td>\n<td style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact;padding:0.3em 0.1em;line-height:14px;text-align:center;width:241.729px\">@Item[6fBNlJqwVA11nLmG]{Undisputed Genius}<br /><br style=\"box-sizing:border-box;-webkit-print-color-adjust:exact\" />@Item[qQ05mvYFoysMQH12]{Unyielding Mind} (1d12)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<h1>Academic Disciplines</h1>\n<h2>Archaeologist</h2>\n<p>Specializing in the study of forgotten civilizations, ancient places, and uncharted lands, Archaeologists bring the light of knowledge to the dark and deadly places of the world. Doing their best to uncover the wisdom of ages long forgotten, they tend to feel a sad kinship with the civilizations they study and go to great lengths not to destroy or offend their memory. For an Archaeologist, the best way to improve the present is to learn from both the mistakes and innovations of the past.</p>\n<p>Archaeologist Features</p>\n<p>3rd Level: @Item[4JK4Brn0jfmT9K4O]{Student of History}, @Item[CzXfbmJFI3OxjaEq]{Adventuring Academic}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Item[SHx4tgK63wI1LdPq]{Daring Determination}</p>\n<p>13th Level: @Item[YQaAtQsSHnV4Vql1]{Lore Master}</p>\n<p>17th Level: @Item[NVJaHCYwPX8HabS8]{Master Archaeologist}</p>\n<h2>Investigator</h2>\n<p>Excelling at unraveling mysteries and uncovering secrets, Investigators possess an uncanny ability to read the intent of others. They often spend their lives working against those who deceive the innocent and take advantage of the common trust. Their considerable intellect and eye for the truth stand in the way of thieves, shapeshifters, and corrupt politicians.</p>\n<p>Investigator Features</p>\n<p>3rd Level: @Item[9zoiwVN5h7ThN72W]{Rough and Tumble}, @Item[Ef93enVp4USdDdKY]{Student of Truth}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Item[x16PtYk1lQcgCMB4]{Astute Defense}, @Item[vfsHTi1M1NZMAZ3g]{Ear to the Ground}</p>\n<p>13th Level: @Item[Aedx9sNo9akoOF3j]{Peerless Focus}</p>\n<p>17th Level: @Item[ALJOI2QbB0VOgenQ]{Master Investigator}</p>\n<h2>Naturalist</h2>\n<p>The Naturalist's classroom begins at the edges of civilization. They study the natural balance of ecosystems and will go to any lengths to maintain that balance. A good Naturalist is a protector of wild plants and animals, however, they will not hesitate to put down a creature that is dangerous. Experts at predicting the weather, identifying toxic and medicinal plants, and tracking animals, Naturalists make for excellent guides.</p>\n<p>Naturalist Features</p>\n<p>3rd Level: @Item[p80Xt6BRgIAa00tF]{Student of Nature}, @Item[suxZORIneA9vK4Df]{Survivalist}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Item[ZbZV8Rbm1OIeozsM]{Adapt &amp; Overcome}</p>\n<p>13th Level: @Item[KKNCcS6cBrwvcRB2]{Call of the Wild}</p>\n<p>17th Level: @Item[mgOb8NdntRrufxj5]{Master Naturalist}</p>\n<h2>Physician</h2>\n<p>Physicians bring their considerable intellect to bear healing the sick and tending to the wounded. They spend their lives studying the anatomy and inner workings of mortal beings and use their knowledge to keep their allies in top condition. Using their medical training, they offer aid to those who don't have access to the luxury of divine or arcane healing magic.</p>\n<p>Physician Features</p>\n<p>3rd Level: @Item[nqV5VSHf6qV965UT]{Student of Medicine}, @Item[qX5ErcOnD15jSBpC]{Combat Medic}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Item[9bzPbYHaKcKzP48g]{Field Doctor}</p>\n<p>13th Level: @Item[QzkmIfFIZkDZnmRK]{Advanced Combat Medic}</p>\n<p>17th Level: @Item[M3ydwgm2Kpdt2G8z]{Master Physician}</p>\n<h2>Tactician</h2>\n<p>Most successful monarchs, conquerors, and revolutions have a master strategist that is responsible for their success on the battlefield. Known as Tacticians, these intelligent leaders are always one step ahead of their enemies and strive to have a plan for every eventuality. They know the strategies that lead to glorious victory, and those that end in utter ruin. Alone, a Tactician is no threat, but with powerful allies to command, they become a formidable force, capable of toppling empires.</p>\n<p>Tactician Features</p>\n<p>3rd Level: @Item[MQgrXH3X9r5DtgKL]{Student of War}, @Item[PwOrhtOq3SbqeY0q]{Tactical Commander}</p>\n<p>6th Level: @Item[g0HnyYNOlnn3aeXG]{Unwavering Resolve}</p>\n<p>13th Level: @Item[MSTcE0AvdUZ1uF8C]{Strategic Genius}</p>\n<p>17th Level: @Item[SbiE3ciIAbIcqjr2]{Master Tactician}</p>\n</section>\n</section>\n</section>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"source":"https://www.gmbinder.com/share/-M0ZVK6ndhFyImQPF_aJ","levels":1,"subclass":"","hitDic